OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly
OL,6,Fdry, bright but rather cloudy evening.
OL,7,FThe rest of the night will remain dry
OL,8,Fwith lengthy clear spells. Moderate to
OL,9,Ffresh southwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FLengthy sunny spells between
OL,12,Fpatchy amounts of cloud. Most places
OL,13,Fwill remain dry, but the odd light
OL,14,Fpassing shower for Shetland is
OL,15,Fpossible. Fresh westerly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,18,Fdry with bright spells or sunny
OL,19,Fspells, risk of showers on Friday.
OL,20,FGentle winds on Wednesday but breezier
OL,21,Fon Thursday and Friday.
